data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in this stunning single-family home that's ready to make your homeownership dreams come true. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and over 2500 finished square feet of thoughtfully designed space, this residence is the perfect blend of luxury and practicality.  This split level home is Nestled in the trees and tucked back from the street where you will find this home offers tons of privacy. Located close to schools, shopping, parks and restaurants, with features that include an inviting open plan with 2 living rooms divided by a 2 sided wood burning fireplace and huge windows that offer tons of sunlight. Newer appliances, granite counter tops throughout, a master bath with heated tile floors and custom tiled shower. There are 3 good sized bedrooms on the upper level including the master. Don't let this opportunity slip through your fingers. Schedule a showing today and take the first step toward making this exceptional property your new home. Your dream home awaits in NW Bismarck! Call your favorite realtor today!
